    protocol: 'Phase-2 neuropathy trials used 4mg subcutaneously daily for 28 days. Research protocols often extend to 12 weeks at 4mg/day, with a 4-week washout between cycles. Some researchers drop to 2mg/day for maintenance after the initial response window.',
