    protocol: 'Clinical Tymlos dosing: 80mcg daily SC for up to 24 months, with transient orthostatic hypotension risk in the first hours after injection, so seated or supine dosing is standard. Research replications follow the same SC route; animal-scale work extrapolates by body weight from the clinical regimen.',
