    protocol: 'Frequently referenced research schedules use 1–2mg per week split into one or two subcutaneous doses. Because the DAC anchor produces continuous receptor occupancy, per-injection microdosing as done with No-DAC is not applicable. Consult the COA reconstitution volume before planning weekly splits.',
