    protocol: 'Research protocols range from 200–500mcg subcutaneously daily for immune-modulatory work to 1mg daily for acute antimicrobial research. Short 1–2 week courses are common for infection models; 4–8 week cycles are standard for chronic-wound or immune-modulation research.',
