    benefits: ["Scale for multi-subject cohort research designs from a single compound lot","Supports parallel dose-response arms without lot-to-lot variation","Appropriate for extended research protocols beyond the 20mg vial window","Single reconstitution minimizes compound-identity overhead across complex studies","Same MRWQEMGYIFYPRKLR mitochondrial peptide chemistry as smaller sizes","Best unit economics realized only when the full vial is consumed in-window"],
