    protocol: 'GLORY-1 titration schedule: 1.5mg weekly for 4 weeks → 3mg for 4 weeks → 4.5mg for 4 weeks → 6mg maintenance. The 6mg weekly dose is reached at week 13 in the full titration arm. GI tolerability drives the titration length — skipping steps produces substantial nausea above what GLP-1-only compounds show.',
