    protocol: 'Published research uses SC administration in the 100–500mcg range per dose, with dose-escalation protocols starting low to assess individual sensitivity. Strong flushing and nausea signals are dose-dependent and mediated by MC3R/MC4R engagement. Research cadences rarely exceed every-other-day administration during active study windows.',
