    protocol: 'Reference research protocols use 200–400mcg subcutaneously post-training two or three times per week, timing administration near the mechanical-loading stimulus MGF is splice-variant-responsive to. Unpegylated MGF, by contrast, is administered locally and more frequently due to its shorter half-life.',
