    protocol: 'Pilot-scale cadences mirror the published or community source — intranasal microgram dosing multiple times daily for CIRS protocols, or IV/inhaled routes at research-specific doses for pulmonary/vascular work. The advantage of the 5mg format is validating cadence on a short horizon before moving to the 10mg extended format if the research plan requires continuity.',
